{% doc %}
  @prompt
    A modern SaaS-style hero section UI design for a Thai signage and printing company website. Left side: clean white space with a large bold headline in Thai and English mix, a gradient CTA button (cyan to indigo to lavender), and three small stat counters below a thin divider line (customers, projects, satisfaction score). Right side: a horizontal auto-scrolling ิbento collage belt of frosted glass product cards. Cards float on a soft gradient background. Two card sizes — tall single cards (portrait) and stacked half-height card pairs — arranged in alternating columns. Each card has a large centered emoji icon and a small label underneath. Cards have white semi-transparent background with subtle border and soft drop shadow. Left and right edges of the belt fade to transparent using gradient masks. Background: transparent but very soft pastel gradient from mint-cyan (
    #ECFEFF) on the left transitioning through cool periwinkle (
    #EEF2FF) to soft lavender (
    #F5F3FF) on the right glow overlay. Three subtle radial glow overlays — cyan glow at left center, purple glow at top right, sky-blue glow at bottom center. Typography: Google Sans Display for headings. Clean, minimal, lots of white space. UI style: glassmorphism cards, soft shadows, rounded corners (radius ~20px), no harsh borders. Light and airy. Modern B2B e-commerce aesthetic. Desktop layout. 16:9 ratio. Color palette: 
    #22D3C8 cyan, 
    #818CF8 indigo, 
    #A78BFA lavender, white cards, pastel background., ปูพื้นหลัง BG เต็มความกว้างตามหน้าจอเลยนะ, ไม่ต้องใส่ bg color เลย ปล่อยใสไป, .hero-h1 em {
      font-style: normal; /*打ล้าง italic default ของ <em> */
    
      /* 1. ใส่ gradient เป็น background ก่อน */
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #22D3C8, #818CF8, #A78BFA);
      background-size: 300%; /* ให้ใหญ่กว่า element เพื่อให้ animation เลื่อนได้ */
    
      /* 2. clip background ให้เหลือแค่รูปทรงของตัวอักษร */
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
    
      /* 3. ทำสีตัวอักษรให้โปร่งใส → เห็น background ที่ clip ไว้แทน */
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      color: transparent; /* fallback */
    
      /* 4. animate background-position ให้ gradient เลื่อนวนไป */
      animation: rbMove 4s linear infinite;
    }
    
    @keyframes rbMove {
      0%   { background-position: 0%; }
      100% { background-position: 300%; }
    }
    ```
    
